{"tid":340340,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【神秘賭神】永利：賭客玩百家樂單月贏7800萬","createTime":"2017-07-29T22:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T14:37:03.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d201ff0a497fd4931e5ccf681ea4ae437f59dd","tid":340340,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T22:43:09.000Z","msg":"神秘賭神再現澳門賭場！《彭博》報道，永利澳門（1128）創辦人兼主席史提芬&bull;永利（Steve Wynn）上周二在分析員電話會議透露，有賭客今年4月在集團旗下永利皇宮玩百家樂，一個月贏走1000萬美元（約7800萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n史提芬&bull;永利表示，有貴賓客（VIP）由周焯華旗下太陽城集團（Suncity）疊馬仔帶入永利皇宮玩百家樂，並贏走逾千萬美元，令賭場今年4月全月虧蝕。史提芬&bull;永利又指這是他50年來遇上「最統計不尋常」（the most statistical anomaly）的事情，更指當時不只一人贏錢。然而，史提芬&bull;永利沒有進一步披露涉及賭客人數與賭客落注金額。<br />\n<br />\n太陽城集團回應《彭博》查詢時表示沒有任何資料可提供。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170729/large/1501335525_2ca5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170729%2Flarge%2F1501335525_2ca5.jpg&h=c036b564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(路透社網站圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57018451&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57018451%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170729&d=S8PwmGUixMtWi6VUmInpDsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=502af46b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57018451%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170729&h=f9365187\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57018451&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170729</a>"},{"pid":"636b28e9172d31ad916c3d2c62ec4f16796a4439","tid":340340,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T23:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"590e112d04282c27abaf4064d4813728bb6db588","tid":340340,"uid":53429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"又黎做promotion"},{"pid":"62a1393f51bf6e073923fab0d29f7fdfb17a4e44","tid":340340,"uid":56236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:10:13.000Z","msg":"師父話賭股唔得，唔論就係佢贏左1000萬美元🤔"},{"pid":"1aa8124dd1ad2a12c4f1da33a8dfc2bdcdb05e20","tid":340340,"uid":126329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"又吹水 省d啦 沒人黎賭喇"},{"pid":"f472aa4490d36bb120afcdff5678ca9695de9e21","tid":340340,"uid":43921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又吹水 省d啦 沒人黎賭喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 客人唔洗多 大客有時一個就夠"}]}